# Drop gallery photographs here.
# Use SEO-friendly filenames, e.g. cape-town-conference-2026.webp
# After dropping a file in:
#   1. Open gallery.html
#   2. Copy a <button class="gallery__item"> block
#   3. Update the <img src> and alt text to match
#   4. (Optional) Add data-full="…" pointing to a higher-res version
# Recommended widths: 800–1600px.
